1954;;The Body Said No!;;British;;Val Guest;;Michael Rennie, Yolande Donlan;;comedy/crime;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Body_Said_No!;;In a British TV studio, Michael Rennie (as himself) is performing live in a dramatic broadcast. On a neighbouring set, cabaret singer Mikki Brent thinks she sees a coded plot being discussed to murder Rennie. Her friends are sceptical, but she warns Rennie, and various adventures and investigations ensue.